::: JACKLE and PHENIOX rush through the forest in there beat modes. JACKLE in 
his large dorlike state, and PHENIOX in her firebird mode. She soars overhead 
and reports to JACKLE who scouts the ground, sniffing for the prey. HELL 
BEAST sent them out to aid Gangon and Brightblade, and they were very close. 
::::

::: JACKLE ::: Ah....Keep north! I have there sent.

::: PHENIOX, overhead ::: I can see blast fire, cmon!

::: The two Predacons rush onward, only to hear a small alram go off. 
According to the scanners...Quickstrike is even closer to the battle. :::

::: JACKLE transforms ::: Ah....our little friend is here, somewhere.

::: PHENIOX lands, still in her beast mode. :::: Hmm, should we pick him off, 
and then go to help Brightblade?

::: JACKLE ::; I think as predacons its out duty to cause destruction where 
ever we can.

::: PHENIOX smiles, and transforms. She takes out her flame thrower pistol, 
points it at a large dead tree, and fires. Within moments the forest begins 
to blaze around them. The Predacons laugh and then proceeded to go to help 
Brightblade, leaving the forest in flames. :::
